title: Alan Moore Collection I- English Invasion
description:
So this is me breaking apart my Massive 29 gig Alan Moore Collection into much easier to to download pieces. 

This torrent is only a bit over 6 gigs and has all the comics Alan Moore wrote before coming to America

Titles include Dark Star, Maxwell The Magic Cat, Sounds,
Marvel UK, Captain Britain, Doctor Who, Night Raven, Star Wars,
2000 AD, IDW, Big Numbers, Miracleman, Monster, BoJeffries Saga, A Small Killing, and Warrior

Please enjoy. Please please please donate to this Kickstarter
